The todolist python script helps you handle a database of things to do.

The todolist table is :
id | timestamp | deadline | genre | subject | detail | done

id : unique id primary key of database entry
timestamp : date and time  of entry in the todolist
deadline : date the thing to do must be done
genre : keyword for letting you know which kind of thing is to do
subject : little description of TODO
detail : Detailled description of TODO
done : Boolean ; if the thing to do was done or not


